enhanced_by.reason: Both methods modify the set of allowed tags, making them complementary for setting up test scenarios.
Both methods involve removing elements (tags or attributes) from the safelist, which can be used to set up specific test conditions.
The method isSafeTag can be used to verify that the tags removed by removeTags are indeed no longer considered safe.
After removing tags, the method isSafeAttribute can be used to ensure that attributes associated with the removed tags are also handled correctly.
